measurement of the signal size as a function of the\ncoordinate parallel to the electric field confirms the prediction that mainly\nelectrons contribute to the signal. Also evidence for the presence of a\npolarisation field was observed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Apr 2015 20:01:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Jul 2015 09:27:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-02"}
